    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>There is a general feeling that increased testing has a salutary effect on the course of the current coronavirus epidemic. We quantify the relationship of testing rate with the doubling time and reproduction number in India, estimate the effect, and use these relationships to make projections for the near future.</jats:p>",
